        Version: 1.05 |
        Status: ✅ A.3 CREDENTIALS AUDIT COMPLETED (Jan 12 re-audit verified: docker-compose files use K8s Secrets pattern with env var references, .env files properly gitignored, all audit findings from Dec 26 confirmed and implemented) |
        Maintainer: All Zencoder Agents (Docker, Coding, Infrastructure)
    </div>

    <!-- QUICK NAVIGATION -->
    <div id="toc" class="row" style="margin: var(--spacing-large) 0; background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.15); padding: var(--spacing-medium); border-left: 4px solid var(--primary-color); border-radius: 4px;">
