            <h3 id="asset-phase1-progress" style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font); font-size: var(--font-size-large);">📊 Phase 1 Progress (Real-Time)</h3>

            <div style="background-color: #e8f5e9; padding: var(--spacing-medium); margin: var(--spacing-medium) 0; border-left: 4px solid #388e3c; border-radius: 4px;">
                <h4 style="color: #388e3c; margin-top: 0;">✅ COMPLETED (Chat 5)</h4>
                <ul style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font); margin: 0;">
                    <li><strong>Comserv::Util::Encryption.pm</strong> - Created with namespace-aware AES-256 encryption
                        <ul>
                            <li>Location: <code>Comserv/lib/Comserv/Util/Encryption.pm</code></li>
                            <li>Public methods: <code>encrypt($plaintext, $namespace)</code>, <code>decrypt($encrypted, $namespace)</code>, <code>get_key($namespace)</code></li>
                            <li>Supports multiple namespaces: proxmox, database, api, default</li>
                            <li>Key management: env var (PREFIX_ENCRYPTION_KEY) or file (.PREFIX_encryption_key)</li>
                            <li>Auto-generates 256-bit random keys if needed</li>
                        </ul>
                    </li>
                    <li><strong>Comserv::Util::ProxmoxCredentials.pm</strong> - Refactored to use Encryption.pm
                        <ul>
                            <li>Removed 100+ lines of duplicate encryption code</li>
                            <li>Now delegates to <code>Encryption->encrypt/decrypt('proxmox')</code></li>
                            <li>Removed: <code>_get_encryption_key()</code>, <code>_encrypt()</code>, <code>_decrypt()</code>, <code>_ensure_config_dir()</code></li>
                            <li>Functionality unchanged - all existing Proxmox credential operations still work</li>
                        </ul>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div style="background-color: #fff9c4; padding: var(--spacing-medium); margin: var(--spacing-medium) 0; border-left: 4px solid #fbc02d; border-radius: 4px;">
                <h4 style="color: #f57f17; margin-top: 0;">⏳ NEXT STEPS (Ordered)</h4>
                <ol style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font); margin: 0;">
                    <li><strong>ApplicationCredentials Database Table</strong> - SQL migration + DBIx::Class result class</li>
                    <li><strong>ApplicationCredentialsAuditLog Table</strong> - For audit trail (pattern from EnvVariableAuditLog)</li>
                    <li><strong>Comserv::Util::CredentialsManager.pm</strong> - Orchestrator using Encryption.pm + tables</li>
                    <li><strong>Diagnostic Controller</strong> - Route: /diagnostic/setup/debug (credentials panel)</li>
                    <li><strong>Diagnostic Template</strong> - UI for database credentials (ency, forager) with test button</li>
                    <li><strong>import_db_credentials.pl</strong> - Script to import COMSERV_DB_* env vars to database</li>
                </ol>
            </div>

