            <h2 id="for-agents" style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font);">8. How AI Agents Use This Document</h2>

            <h3 style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font); font-size: var(--font-size-large);">When Starting a Credential-Related Task:</h3>
            <ol style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font);">
                <li>Read Section 4 (Quick Reference Table) to understand current state</li>
                <li>Find your task in Section 3 (Management Plan) - identify which phase</li>
                <li>Follow the phase roadmap - don't skip steps</li>
                <li><strong>IMPORTANT:</strong> Use <code>ask_questions()</code> before making changes to confirm approach</li>
                <li>Update this document after completing work:
                    <ul>
                        <li>Add what you implemented</li>
                        <li>Update status in Timeline (Section 6)</li>
                        <li>Add any blockers or learnings</li>
                        <li>Increment page_version in META</li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
            </ol>

            <h3 style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font); font-size: var(--font-size-large);">Example: "Add Cloudflare Support"</h3>
            <ol style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font);">
                <li>Read Section 2.2 (Current: "not yet implemented")</li>
                <li>Reference Section 3, Phase 2 (Unified Credential Storage)</li>
                <li>Ask questions: "Should we extend ProxmoxCredentials or create new APICredentials module?"</li>
                <li>Create implementation based on user feedback</li>
                <li>Update Section 2.2 table to mark as ✅ implemented</li>
                <li>Update this document with new version number</li>
            </ol>

            <div style="background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.15); border-left: 4px solid var(--warning-color); padding: var(--spacing-medium); margin: var(--spacing-small) 0; border-radius: 4px;">
                <h3 style="color: var(--warning-color); margin-top: 0;">🔴 Blocking Issues to Escalate:</h3>
                <ul style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font); margin-bottom: 0;">
                    <li>Chicken-and-egg problem (credentials needed to load credentials)</li>
                    <li>Security audit failing</li>
                    <li>Encryption key rotation questions</li>
                    <li>Multi-database credential conflicts</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

